des:
With KEYCO air Skill, track your air condition (Air Quality, temperature, humidity & Discomfort Level) of your house with your voice now!

1.You can check the air condition of your house by KEYCO air APP anytime and anywhere.
2.KEYCO air can be placed anywhere in the house(Kitchen,living room etc.).
3.KEYCO air also provides severity alerts and notifications to keep you safe and healthy.

To get started, you will need to have a KEYCO air account enabled and a KEYCO air device.

Don't have KEYCO air. Buy here http://www.mykeyco.com
